:name: s32k118
:description: This script runs Steering Board demo on s32k118

using sysbus

:Creation of Machine 
mach create "s32k118_Board"
machine LoadPlatformDescription @renode_sim/Board/s32k118_Board.repl

:Open an analyzer for the uart port
:showAnalyzer sysbus.lpuart0

:Put the location of the BinaryShell 
$bin?=@renode_sim/Binary/blink_led.elf


:Creation of Macros every time I request the macro it executes and load the code
macro reset
"""
    sysbus LoadELF $bin
"""
runMacro $reset

:logLevel -1 portB.LED1

:start the GDB server on port 3333 
machine StartGdbServer 3333